# See https://docs.github.com/articles/about-codeowners
#
# Ownership lives on the @foolswithtools/maintainers team — to grant
# review-required ownership to a new maintainer, add them to the team
# (Org → Teams → maintainers) rather than editing this file.

# Default owner for every file.
*                    @foolswithtools/maintainers

# Highest-stakes paths get the same review (kept explicit for clarity).
/.github/            @foolswithtools/maintainers
/infra/              @foolswithtools/maintainers
/runtime/            @foolswithtools/maintainers
/scripts/            @foolswithtools/maintainers

# Documentation that's the contract with downstream forks and LLM agents.
/CLAUDE.md           @foolswithtools/maintainers
/docs/adr/           @foolswithtools/maintainers
/.upstream-sync.toml @foolswithtools/maintainers
